"""
    unity test for AF-SIW object
    """
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    af1 = wg.AF_SIW(COPPER, D5880, 0.0024, 0)
af1 = wg.AF_SIW(COPPER, D5880, 0.0024, 0.0002)
af1.set_width(0.00694)
assert round(af1.f_c * 1e-09, 1) == 14.6
af1.set_fc(17000000000.0)
assert round(1000 * af1.width, 1) == 5.9
assert af1.calc_a_d(15000000000.0) == 0
assert round(af1.calc_ksr(20000000000.0), 6) == 1
af1.f_c = 0
af1.print_info()
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    af1.calc_fc(0, 1)
